    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Dorifto!</strong></i> is an arcade driving experience featuring unique drifting physics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/dbedc5ebe457d1c2ce48878b4b404d6e.poster.avif?t=1769466546\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/dbedc5ebe457d1c2ce48878b4b404d6e.webm?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/dbedc5ebe457d1c2ce48878b4b404d6e.mp4?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in <strong>Time Trials</strong> and unique <strong>Challenges</strong> across 9+ stages as you master the sideways slide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/6aa5d0078dca2c23818b7408bdd16a3b.poster.avif?t=1769466546\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/6aa5d0078dca2c23818b7408bdd16a3b.webm?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/6aa5d0078dca2c23818b7408bdd16a3b.mp4?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock <strong>Mechanical Mods</strong> and <strong>Customize </strong>your ride and turn your hand-me-down beater into an absolute demon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/f4cdc2e4106d85616252b22fc8597159.poster.avif?t=1769466546\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/f4cdc2e4106d85616252b22fc8597159.webm?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/f4cdc2e4106d85616252b22fc8597159.mp4?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a drifting legend by earning a top spot on the global leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/b48dfd6d425a98108a9a7e490ae2fafe.poster.avif?t=1769466546\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/b48dfd6d425a98108a9a7e490ae2fafe.webm?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182560/extras/b48dfd6d425a98108a9a7e490ae2fafe.mp4?t=1769466546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
